      <title>真主党向以色列开火，危及美国斡旋的停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/hezbollah-fires-toward-israel-as-skirmishes-mar-cease-fire-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[真主党宣称对以色列发动了自美国支持的停火计划生效不到一周以来的首次袭击，这促使以色列官员誓言将作出强烈回应，这是迄今为止对黎巴嫩停火协议最严重的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/hezbollah-fires-toward-israel-as-skirmishes-mar-cease-fire-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:06:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登赦免儿子可能会玷污其政治遗产并增强特朗普的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/biden-s-pardon-of-son-threatens-to-tarnish-legacy-empower-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登公开为赦免儿子的决定辩解，指责司法部进行政治针对，这可能会破坏他数十年从政生涯中精心树立的形象：一个诚实的经纪人，其主要忠诚是保护美国关键机构的神圣性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/biden-s-pardon-of-son-threatens-to-tarnish-legacy-empower-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腐败丑闻给哥伦比亚财政部长带来更多压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/corruption-scandal-adds-to-pressure-on-colombia-s-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚财政部长因涉嫌腐败丑闻而受到新的指控，在政府试图应对日益加深的财政危机之际，这给总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗带来了更多麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/corruption-scandal-adds-to-pressure-on-colombia-s-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:24:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果法国政府在预算摊牌后倒台，会发生什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/what-happens-if-french-government-falls-after-budget-showdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府有可能在本周末前垮台，并可能带来惨痛的经济和金融后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/what-happens-if-french-government-falls-after-budget-showdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚法院批准亲俄候选人参加决选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/romania-s-top-court-clears-pro-russia-candidate-for-runoff-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最高法院确认了一场关键总统选举的结果，批准亲俄候选人参加这场对位于北约东翼的罗马尼亚具有重大地缘政治意义的决选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/romania-s-top-court-clears-pro-russia-candidate-for-runoff-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 17:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚反对派推进，阿萨德和伊朗面临艰难抉择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/syria-war-is-president-assad-going-to-lose-to-rebel-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚的反政府武装正试图扩大近期的战果并夺取更多政府控制的领土，这引发了人们对总统巴沙尔·阿萨德是否能够继续掌权的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/syria-war-is-president-assad-going-to-lose-to-rebel-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟抗议冲突后格鲁吉亚总理拒绝与反对派进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/georgia-premier-rules-out-talks-with-opposition-after-eu-protest-clashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚总理排除了与反对派举行会谈的可能性，此前首都连续四晚的暴力冲突导致拉里兑美元汇率跌至两年来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/georgia-premier-rules-out-talks-with-opposition-after-eu-protest-clashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国极右翼企图通过新预算法推翻政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/far-right-to-back-no-confidence-motion-against-french-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 未能满足玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 对新预算的要求，玛丽娜·勒庞誓言要推翻巴尼耶政府，这威胁到法国的财政和政治稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/far-right-to-back-no-confidence-motion-against-french-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国希望加强军事供应链以达到 2.5% 的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/uk-looks-to-bolster-military-supply-chain-ahead-of-2-5-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正准备就何时增加国防开支做出更明确的承诺，与此同时，英国将通过“实战演习”来评估其国内供应链和军队能否抵御未来的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/uk-looks-to-bolster-military-supply-chain-ahead-of-2-5-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州计划以 2500 万美元诉讼的方式反对特朗普的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/california-eyes-25-million-legal-battle-against-trump-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 希望拨款 2500 万美元，派遣一批律师来挑战当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 最激进的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/california-eyes-25-million-legal-battle-against-trump-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
